Process called "assess_ethical_risks" that takes operation as Dictionary and violations as List[Dictionary] returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_ethical_mitigations" that takes violations as List[Dictionary] returns List[String]
Process called "copy_dictionary" that takes dict as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "evaluate_ethical_constraint" that takes action as Dictionary and constraint as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "apply_ethical_mitigation" that takes action as Dictionary and constraint as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "all_constraints_satisfied" that takes results as List[Dictionary] returns Boolean
